0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;爱泼斯坦档案&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;高盛首席执行官所罗门要求鲁姆勒留下，尽管杰弗里·爱泼斯坦感到愤怒&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;她定于本月辞职，因为她与被定罪的性犯罪者的沟通受到越来越多的审查。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国参议院的共和党人&lt;/strong&gt;在三年内推动了一项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/s73GgN4Vhsm1MDiW6HAhNrVc8Q2tGQ80GH7EmQoo7yd88FgfgNodpnGYeqHKfVvGTD3n_yOqHGzUHwn6Ou2VhgVVzPwZo6_wt1TT8YEddF_qcLHzMbdHAYM4YY6YiVlAJHKILQSWSM-prsqAlNh4S4qo8WeoPaGU2uQ_TiPduZ2aQDCI083qY93ccy38CiaNXsQnCVfutMWihWA064Qmh1_To-CsUQGesVS7NmlRy4O_0ppA2CrEP6cVTi7EAqJb8KQrGGPuoSSXeOA1mX3C86TwLvoY9TdNZa7Y2w9SAtZ7jC9ml67Ndqv16qzks0qew_3BR2GvaAdBCA9QzoLLDnwApJASsh6Zo-0hjzDbhcacdyP5FabdYenhXkZ8jonXdQAiQ6ZJaToKInt_BfGKFYhMxC873BPhrWyRRGRNeyEeL-La6kE_-5wbliUEH4VYIUFhZk1y04Uggy5RMluHIqTfipTEYqZMZaLH0Ir9WjWOkrfaPSwGywQUEuAkFTZ8aJS_NSXJa-7YYlwsyi1o7y9fyQKw8A/czUQzaCGG4k0Xn2ADFeFcLYc9UdZjvh_/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="参议院在 18 亿美元资金纠纷后通过移民法案"&gt;为移民、海关执法和边境巡逻机构提供资金的&lt;/a&gt;法案，但没有要求他们的特工遵守&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8K-zRYqSijJBy_3r8NiJDmh6YTmy9afp9Tj0CJw6lu54RbGrWaEuorG-ShwrqLMBopZyiJ5Z4EdpwDZZ4CibfOMybUuFWYKruaGnj_Li68RPtg9jkFtind4IpOT_z2vn1dmG6203cFTOM4-80qTp-oKm7uKpjWysvW6nKBE_x-wB2UxFxbpeVnkFWlvkv9qHsDPhUHXFvKGb4q6EC4tb25bGxz6tDqbtmIU-MtmVqEK2ieQ91d6jSN6k9x_jUB2IU8Fm5MB8aRpdDnh5s5fS1X1Re-QSfUUOOYRJzb__5izGkPcGmeglj_XwGkv2yeFwUzgV-E6CGxM4vF